<div class="pa"><div class="i"><img class="im" src="~@img/02109.png"></div><div class="t"><p>大朵墓地铃兰</p><br>在地下墓地绽放的白色花朵，<br>其中较大朵的一种。<br><br>能将骨灰强化至＋１０。<br><br>自古以来，大朵铃兰用于慰借英灵──<br>向最伟大的死亡献上花朵，<br>祈祷英雄最终能化为神话。<br>能将骨灰强化至＋１０</div><div class="t"><p>墓すずらんの大輪</p><br>地下墓地に咲く白い花<br>その大粒の一輪<br><br>遺灰を＋１０に強化できる<br><br>古来、大輪は英霊を慰めるとされ<br>最も偉大な死に手向けられる<br>やがて神話となるように<br><br>遺灰を＋１０に強化できる</div><div class="t"><p>Great Grave Glovewort</p><br>White flower that blooms in catacombs.<br>An especially large specimen.<br><br>Strengthens ashes to +10.<br><br>Since times of old, large gloveworts were used to comfort heroic spirits. Given in tribute to those who died the most glorious of deaths, in the hope their stories would become legend.<br>Strengthen ashes to +10</div></div>
